    {
      "para_id": "Q001120.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninĝirsu , Enlil's warrior ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001120.3",
      "line_range": "3",
      "translation": "(3) En-ana-tum , ruler of Lagaš , chosen by Nanše in the heart , chief governor of Ninĝirsu , child of En-metena , ruler of Lagaš , restored ( Ninĝirsu's ) brewery for Ninĝirsu ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001120.16",
      "line_range": "16",
      "translation": "(16) The personal god of En-ana-tum , the restorer of Ninĝirsu's brewery , is Šul-MUŠxPA ."
    }
  ],
